    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-10-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-10-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="59"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d59">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-10-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 21, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received October 21.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson represents the situation as unchanged. He reports repeated failures
                    of the insurgents in their attempts to disembark forces, and the daily
                    continuance of bombardment between the forts. He announces the arrival on this
                    day of the U. S. S. <hi rend="italic">Newark.</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
